{"tid":1172820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果6/9會出黎既話 希望大家吸收下雨傘既失敗經驗","createTime":"2019-05-26T16:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T15:55:23.000Z","uid":246686,"like":72,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e84f4e4290fdc095b56f70967d6d25ff8c5370e4","tid":1172820,"uid":246686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"1. 組織問題<br />\n2014年果時雖然好成功咁令好多人出黎 但事實上個組織好分散<br />\n依個係social media時代既社會運動特徵 動員快 但容易組織鬆散<br />\n雖然大家都出左黎 其實有好多唔同既群體 大台/ 學聯/ 有D radical D既/ 自發行動既<br />\n點樣&quot;統一戰線&quot; (共產黨理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 好重要<br />\ne.g. 你地點選擇個地點?個地點有咩影響?<br />\n<br />\n同埋 大家要諗下當日點解有咁多人出黎 e.g. 學生身份既黃之鋒比人拉/煙霧彈<br />\n而6/9 會唔會有可能重現到依D因素? 或者有咩其他新既因素說服令人一定要出?<br />\n決定要出既人 都最好同身邊既人討論下 比多D關注件事<br />\n唔多人出黎既話 777當你冇到<br />\n<br />\n2. 應對黑警<br />\n大家都記得2014年黑警點對手無寸鐵既市民 <br />\n麻煩大家都收起對黑警左膠式期許 亦都唔好浪費力量說服/感化佢地 <br />\ne.g. &quot;佢地有好多都係好人&quot;,&quot;身在曹營心在漢&quot;, 送支花比黑警/hug一hug佢地<br />\n我明白事實上可能警隊入面有E D人 但你作為市民 你既角色一定同警察有衝突<br />\n革命不是請客食飯 煩請大家都認清楚邊個朋友邊個敵人<br />\n<br />\n根據小弟觀察 928當中最高潮果時<br />\n黑警有舉橙布威脅開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府有叫醫院準備接收傷者 (maybe even 死者?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201409/28/P201409280831.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201409%2F28%2FP201409280831.htm&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=a0f98685\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201409/28/P201409280831.htm</a><br />\n消息會封鎖 --&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">果時上網慢左 上高登慢左十倍</span> (你地諗下到時6/9 連登會點?)<br />\n謠言滿天飛 e.g. 果時網上面曾經傳有老解坦克入隧道<br />\n出黎既巴絲要確保有好既 communication channel<br />\n謠言詳見網典: <a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E4%B9%8B%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BexpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=155b8b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E4%B9%8B%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 抗爭常識同合作行動<br />\n依點2014年果時都有人提出D 人人都要有D抗爭既常識<br />\n例如: 大家唔好落單 落單既就小心係暗角比人打/ 比人拉<br />\n比人拉左既巴絲都要識保護自己 e.g. 落口供咪講野<br />\n對於抗爭 唔該大家亦都有個明確既目標 咪打飛機式咁自我安慰<br />\ne.g. 迫到政府同我地傾算嬴左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 逃犯條例有讓步啦收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而2014年果時雖然自發 但大家都有好多分工 有人送水 有人比野食 etc..<br />\n依D 互相合作係十分之緊要<br />\n2014年果時我仲讀緊書 望住咁多人出黎但無疾而終好痛心<br />\n失敗有一部分係我地自己責任 亦香港人都少經歷大型社會運動<br />\n拋磚引玉 大家有多D deliberation 到時出黎會準備好D 希望6/9見到你"},{"pid":"f839c352345f3c95c5fa1bebe5179bbe9c019e0b","tid":1172820,"uid":246686,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"屌你咁快有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f91b8fd1326251f1c0c7f53d14f602b3306f76","tid":1172820,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d3b3a9ead2be0faedf8a0c744d9f6afebc02a06f","tid":1172820,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:00:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"079380dbcfd8d3272332ecc13082a87d1b18a3ad","tid":1172820,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9a8506d77eb030edd32e3e79081bebdc727159","tid":1172820,"uid":61396,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"需要運動戰<br />\n不是死守 <br />\n<br />\n警察 人數不足<br />\n集結需要時間<br />\n<br />\n如佔領完mk 比人攻時<br />\n行後佔領尖佐 隧道<br />\n<br />\n佔唔到金 佔銅或中環<br />\n<br />\n一玩運動戰<br />\n成個香港都停止<br />\n<br />\n係地鐵 轉車站 <br />\n一百幾十人企係車門口<br />\n唔比開車 <br />\n<br />\n只係太多人 覺得玩堡壘戰<br />\n（死守 ）先叫成功"},{"pid":"17208e8e89036ec1185c4107cbd38672c2032da6","tid":1172820,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"telegram channel散播消息有無得諗？"},{"pid":"0143f4e18296e4fcc26d8acc9e6e8c5cc70c3a0c","tid":1172820,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你口中既「吸收 雨傘/佔中 失敗經驗」冇一part系講 提防泛民大台/陰謀論/散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0aa4e489b1c1a80187730d260f45b64981e82e","tid":1172820,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32afd58f4af3c5b49f3fd9102db77abda91c2822","tid":1172820,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17208e8e89036ec1185c4107cbd38672c2032da6","tid":1172820,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"telegram channel散播消息有無得諗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"要預差佬都收到同準備應對部署"},{"pid":"92cd2d39c0ce6cfa0e18387aaf0019b55440ccff","tid":1172820,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4a3a08121fc27e3e89b5e49f7b1e4b979ddcbc0","tid":1172820,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32afd58f4af3c5b49f3fd9102db77abda91c2822","tid":1172820,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17208e8e89036ec1185c4107cbd38672c2032da6","tid":1172820,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"telegram channel散播消息有無得諗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"要預差佬都收到同準備應對部署"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"其實所有途徑都會<br />\n